
 ARTIST:   Sonic Boom Six
 TITLE:    Play On (Bonus DVD)
 DATE:     12-15-2008
 QUALITY:  DVD
 GENRE:    Punk/Ska
 ARCHIVES: 9x50
 VIDEO:    untouched
 AUDIO:    LPCM 2.0
 STRIPPEd: nothing 
 SOURCE:   Retail DVD

 NOTES: Music video of Sound of a Revolution. This bonus
 disc was sent along with preorders of the new remix
 and rarities album by ska/punk/dub pioneers Sonic
 Boom Six from Manchester.

 So, Play On then… On the first CD we have Arcade Perfected… 
 the entire album of Arcade Perfect completely remixed in 
 all kinda stylee from Dub to Drum n Bass to Dubstep to 
 Plonkelectro(!) from the likes of our very own Ben Boom, 
 Tim G, DJ Sonar, High Rankin, DJ BC, Dan from Skindred and 
 much more. Up now on the myspace is Ben’s mix of ‘Sound of 
 a Revolution’. Have a listen.

 The second disc is chockfull of rarities, demos, live 
 sessions and unreleased tunes. We’ve really scraped the 
 plate to find stuff that fits the standard of the first 
 disc and have included lots of good stuff like the infamous 
 ‘lost song’ ‘We Wanna War’ and some things never heard before 
 by anyone, anywhere. The new, previously unreleased recording 
 ‘Play On’ is up on the myspace now. Have a listen!

 TRACKLIST:
 1. Sound of a Revolution